<task id="SPE-044" project="SDAP SPE Admin App">
  <metadata>
    <title>Deploy Code Page to Dataverse</title>
    <status>completed</status>
    <estimated-effort>2h</estimated-effort>
    <tags>deploy, code-page, dataverse, phase-1</tags>
    <phase>1</phase>
    <dependencies>SPE-042</dependencies>
  </metadata>
  <prompt>Deploy the built SPE Admin App code page (dist/speadmin.html) as a Dataverse web resource. Upload it as sprk_speadmin, publish customizations, and verify it is accessible from the Dataverse sitemap.</prompt>
  <role>Dataverse developer with web resource deployment experience</role>
  <goal>The sprk_speadmin web resource is published in Dataverse and accessible from the sitemap entry created in task SPE-004.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-006">Code pages are deployed as single-file HTML web resources to Dataverse.</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/skills/code-page-deploy/SKILL.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>
  <context>
    <background>The SPE Admin App is a React 18 code page that gets deployed as a Dataverse web resource. The deployment process uploads the single HTML file to Dataverse and publishes customizations so it becomes available to users. The sitemap entry (created in task SPE-004) points to this web resource.</background>
  </context>
  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="upload">Deploy dist/speadmin.html as the sprk_speadmin web resource to Dataverse.</step>
    <step order="2" name="publish">Publish all customizations to make the web resource available.</step>
    <step order="3" name="verify-sitemap">Verify the web resource is accessible from the Dataverse sitemap.</step>
    <step order="4" name="test-load">Open the admin app from the sitemap and verify it loads without errors.</step>
  </steps>
  <outputs>
    <output type="code">Dataverse web resource: sprk_speadmin</output>
  </outputs>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">Web resource sprk_speadmin is published in Dataverse.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Admin app is accessible from the Dataverse sitemap.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
